title: FANTOM Listing: Add xBOO market
body:
Intro: This is a vote to list xBOO on C.R.E.A.M. Fantom market with a Collateral Factor and Collateral Cap.
Proposal: Listing Committee
Rational: First mover advantage

For: 
Add xBOO market with Collateral Factor: 60% and Collateral Cap: $3M

Against: 
Do not make any changes to FANTOM market.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
